channel.title: [REQ] Emo/Anime girl leaning on wall
channel.description: So, apparently google/bing image search hates me. I'm trying to find, or have someone make, a anime emo girl, that's leaning on what would appear to be a wall. I'd rather the wall not be there, as I want to use it for my tumblr background. She'd be leaning on the left hand side of the computer screen\browser. Thanks. Width: 400px max height: 1200px max Colors: Dark, but aside from that, it doesn't matter. The background of my tumblr is black. Other: cute please.
